text: Great pizza! Got it take out while passing through Pendleton! Johnathan was the man and helped us split the checks up and bought us some stickers from the sticker machine! Overall a great place

text: I ordered a pizza online on 10/25 and finished the order around 7:30 pm, I then received an email saying the order will be delivered at 8:30 pm I didn't receive my order until 9pm and the pizza was not hot anymore.
